mssql-scripter

→ development/databases/SQL-Server/Management-Studio

*Azure Data Studio* is a light-weight editor that can run on-demand SQL queries, view and save results as text,
→ development/languages/JavaScript/JSON, or → Microsoft/Office/Excel[Excel].

SQL Server Data Tools

{ Tools that are useful in migration scenarios

  *Database Experimentation Assistant (DEA) to* evaluate a given workload on a targeted → development/databases/SQL-Server/versions[SQL Server version], especially before upgrading.

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/Data-Migration-Assistant to detect compatibility issues in newer SQL Server versions.

  Distributed Replay (→ Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-SQL-Server/version/Tools/Binn/DPreplay_exe)

  ssbdiagnose (→ Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-SQL-Server/version/Tools/Binn/SSBDiagnose_exe) to find issues with *Service Broker* conversations or configuration issues with Service Broker services.

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/Migration-Assistant[SQL Server Migration Assistant].

}
